sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Customer
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as NestJS API
  participant W as Rebuild Worker
  participant N as Netlify
  participant DB as Postgres
  C->>FE: Submit own website URL
  FE->>API: importWebsite(projectId,url)
  API->>DB: Create import job
  API->>W: Queue rebuild
  W->>W: Crawl HTML/CSS/assets/content
  W->>W: Map to React components
  W->>W: Improve SEO/CTA/mobile/speed
  W->>N: Deploy staging preview noindex
  W->>DB: Save preview URL
  FE->>C: Show preview
  C->>FE: Add notes or approve
